# HEARTBEAT.md

How to advance work across turns without excess chatter.

- Work until the user’s goal is met or they stop you.
- State progress when a meaningful milestone completes.
- Continue the next step without re-explaining the whole plan each turn.
- Stop when the goal is satisfied or the user signals done.
- Add dated checklist items below only when the operator wants recurring checks; otherwise keep this file empty.
